General Assembly House Joint
Resolution No. 64
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 3095
Referred to Committee on Executive and Legislative Nominations
Introduced by:
REP. CONCEPCION, 4th Dist.
SEN. DUFF, 25th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF GERALD WEINER
OF WOODBRIDGE TO BE REAPPOINTED A MEMBER OF THE STATE
DEPARTMENT OF EDUCATION ARBITRATION PANEL.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the nomination by His Excellency, the Governor, of Gerald
2 Weiner of Woodbridge, to be reappointed a member of the State
3 Department of Education Arbitration Panel, as a neutral arbitrator, to
4 serve a term ending June 30, 2029, or until a successor is appointed and
5 has qualified, whichever is longer, is hereby approved and confirmed.
LCO No. 3095 1 of 1

